<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Zulabike · Campinas → Manaus</title>
<!--
  ===========================================================================
  ZULABIKE — one-pager de captação (Campinas → Manaus)
  COMO USAR NO WIX:
    Opção 1 (mais simples): cole este arquivo inteiro num elemento
      "Incorporar > Incorporar um site / HTML iframe" (modo "Código").
    Opção 2 (mais leve): suba as fotos na Mídia do Wix e troque cada
      bloco  src="data:image..."  pela URL da imagem hospedada no Wix.
  ATUALIZAR O TERMOMETRO: mude só a linha  const ARRECADADO = ...  lá embaixo.
  TESTE O PIX antes de publicar: escaneie o QR com o app do seu banco e
    confirme que aparece "ZWI MOJZESZOWICZ".
  ===========================================================================
-->
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,400;9..144,600;9..144,900&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --night:#0A1733; --night2:#0E2050; --blue:#3D5BFF; --bluelogo:#2B33E0;
    --paper:#F6F2E9; --ink:#1A2236; --muted:#6A7385; --gold:#C8A028; --goldlt:#E6C964;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
  body{margin:0;background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);
    font-family:Inter,-apple-system,system-ui,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;font-size:17px}
  .wrap{max-width:660px;margin:0 auto;position:relative}
  h1,h2,h3,.disp{font-family:Fraunces,Georgia,serif;font-weight:900;line-height:1.07;
    letter-spacing:-.01em;margin:0}
  p{margin:0 0 1em}
  .eyebrow{font-family:Inter;font-weight:700;font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:.18em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blue);margin:0 0 .9rem}
  .night .eyebrow{color:var(--goldlt)}
  section{padding:62px 26px}
  .quote{font-family:Fraunces;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-size:1.34rem;
    line-height:1.34;color:var(--ink)}
  .night .quote{color:#EAF0FF}

  /* ---------- starfield (assinatura, puxada da logo) ---------- */
  .night{position:relative;background:
      radial-gradient(1100px 520px at 78% -8%, #16307a 0%, rgba(22,48,122,0) 60%),
      linear-gradient(180deg,#0B1A3E 0%, var(--night) 70%);
    color:#EAF0FF;overflow:hidden}
  .night .stars{position:absolute;inset:0;pointer-events:none;opacity:.9;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(1.4px 1.4px at 12% 22%,#fff,transparent),
      radial-gradient(1.2px 1.2px at 28% 64%,#cfe0ff,transparent),
      radial-gradient(1.6px 1.6px at 47% 14%,#fff,transparent),
      radial-gradient(1.1px 1.1px at 63% 48%,#fff,transparent),
      radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 81% 30%,#dce8ff,transparent),
      radial-gradient(1.2px 1.2px at 90% 70%,#fff,transparent),
      radial-gradient(1.1px 1.1px at 36% 86%,#fff,transparent),
      radial-gradient(1.3px 1.3px at 71% 82%,#cfe0ff,transparent);}
  .night > *{position:relative;z-index:1}

  /* ---------- hero ---------- */
  .hero{padding:0;min-height:100svh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;
    justify-content:flex-end;color:#fff;position:relative;isolation:isolate}
  .hero .ph{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;
    object-position:32% 38%;z-index:-2}
  .hero::after{content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:-1;background:
     linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(8,16,40,.30) 0%, rgba(8,16,40,.12) 30%,
       rgba(8,16,40,.55) 68%, rgba(8,16,40,.92) 100%)}
  .hero .top{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;display:flex;align-items:center;
    gap:12px;padding:20px 26px;z-index:2}
  .hero .top img{width:54px;height:54px;filter:drop-shadow(0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.4))}
  .hero .top b{font-family:Inter;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;font-size:.78rem;
    text-transform:uppercase}
  .hero .top b span{display:block;font-weight:500;opacity:.85;font-size:.62rem;letter-spacing:.3em}
  .hero .inner{padding:0 26px 46px}
  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(2.5rem,9vw,3.7rem);text-shadow:0 2px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.45)}
  .hero .lead{font-size:1.06rem;margin:18px 0 8px;max-width:30ch;
    text-shadow:0 1px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.6)}
  .hero .facts{font-family:Inter;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.02em;font-size:1.04rem;
    margin:2px 0 26px}
  .hero .facts span{color:var(--goldlt)}
  .cta{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.6em;background:var(--gold);
    color:#1a1400;font-family:Inter;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;text-decoration:none;
    padding:15px 26px;border-radius:999px;border:0;cursor:pointer;
    box-shadow:0 6px 22px rgba(200,160,40,.4);transition:transform .15s,box-shadow .15s}
  .cta:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(200,160,40,.5)}
  .cta.ghost{background:transparent;color:#fff;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.55);
    box-shadow:none}

  /* ---------- quem ---------- */
  .figute{margin:0 0 26px;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;
    box-shadow:0 14px 34px rgba(20,30,60,.18)}
  .figute img{width:100%;display:block}
  .figute figcaption{font-size:.84rem;color:var(--muted);padding:10px 14px;background:#fff}
  .role{font-family:Inter;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.04em;color:var(--blue);
    margin:0 0 6px;font-size:.96rem}

  /* ---------- estrada / mapa ---------- */
  .map{background:#fff;border-radius:14px;padding:10px 8px 4px;
    box-shadow:0 14px 34px rgba(20,30,60,.14);margin:6px 0 22px}
  .map svg{width:100%;height:auto;display:block}
  ul.legend{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;font-size:.98rem}
  ul.legend li{padding:9px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(26,34,54,.10)}
  ul.legend li:last-child{border:0}
  ul.legend b{font-family:Fraunces;font-weight:600}

  /* ---------- por que ---------- */
  .big{font-size:clamp(1.7rem,6vw,2.3rem);line-height:1.16;margin:0 0 22px}
  .attrib{font-family:Inter;font-style:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:.92rem;
    color:var(--goldlt);display:block;margin-top:.7em}

  /* ---------- equivalencia (signature) ---------- */
  .equation{padding:54px 26px;text-align:center}
  .equation .n{font-family:Fraunces;font-weight:900;font-size:clamp(2.4rem,11vw,4rem);
    color:var(--goldlt);line-height:.98;letter-spacing:-.02em}
  .equation .x{font-family:Inter;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.06em;color:#9fb2e6;
    font-size:.82rem;text-transform:uppercase;margin:6px 0}
  .equation .k{font-family:Fraunces;font-weight:600;font-style:italic;font-size:1.5rem;
    color:#fff;margin-top:14px}

  /* ---------- apoiar ---------- */
  .meter{background:#fff;border-radius:16px;padding:24px 22px;
    box-shadow:0 14px 34px rgba(20,30,60,.16);margin:0 0 26px}
  .meter .row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:10px}
  .meter .raised{font-family:Fraunces;font-weight:900;font-size:1.9rem;color:var(--ink)}
  .meter .goal{font-family:Inter;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);font-size:.92rem}
  .bar{height:16px;background:#ECE6D6;border-radius:999px;overflow:hidden}
  .bar > i{display:block;height:100%;width:0;border-radius:999px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gold),var(--goldlt));
    transition:width 1.1s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1)}
  .meter .days{font-family:Inter;font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:10px}
  .pixcard{background:var(--night2);border-radius:16px;padding:24px 22px;text-align:center;
    border:1px solid rgba(122,150,255,.25)}
  .pixcard .qr{background:#fff;border-radius:12px;padding:12px;display:inline-block;width:190px}
  .pixcard .qr svg{width:100%;height:auto;display:block}
  .pixcard .lbl{font-family:Inter;font-weight:600;font-size:.74rem;letter-spacing:.16em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:#9fb2e6;margin:16px 0 4px}
  .pixcard .key{font-family:Inter;font-weight:700;font-size:1.16rem;color:#fff;
    letter-spacing:.02em}
  .copy{margin-top:14px;background:#fff;color:var(--night);border:0;border-radius:999px;
    font-family:Inter;font-weight:700;font-size:.94rem;padding:12px 22px;cursor:pointer;
    transition:transform .15s}
  .copy:hover{transform:translateY(-2px)}
  .sustain{display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:center;margin:0 0 24px;
    background:#fff;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;
    box-shadow:0 14px 34px rgba(20,30,60,.14)}
  .sustain img{width:42%;align-self:stretch;object-fit:cover;object-position:50% 30%}
  .sustain div{padding:18px 16px 18px 0}
  .sustain p{margin:0;font-size:.98rem}
  .sustain b{font-family:Fraunces;font-weight:900;font-size:1.16rem;display:block;margin-top:4px}

  /* ---------- acompanhe / footer ---------- */
  .follow{text-align:center}
  .follow a.ig{font-family:Fraunces;font-weight:900;font-size:1.7rem;color:#fff;
    text-decoration:none;border-bottom:3px solid var(--gold)}
  footer{background:var(--night);color:#8fa0c8;text-align:center;padding:30px 26px;
    font-size:.82rem}
  footer .lg{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:8px}
  footer img{width:30px;height:30px}
  footer b{color:#cdd8f5;font-family:Inter;letter-spacing:.18em;font-size:.74rem;text-transform:uppercase}

  /* reveal */
  .rv{opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease}
  .rv.in{opacity:1;transform:none}
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){
    .rv{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}
    .bar>i{transition:none}
    html{scroll-behavior:auto}
  }
  @media (max-width:430px){ section{padding:48px 20px} .hero .inner{padding:0 20px 38px} }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
  <header class="hero">
    <img class="ph" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Zwi Mojzeszowicz, de capacete e barba branca, sorrindo numa formação rochosa de deserto durante uma viagem de bicicleta">
    <div class="top">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Logo Zulabike">
      <b>Zulabike<span>no limits</span></b>
    </div>
    <div class="inner">
      <h1>Até onde dá<br>para ir de<br>bicicleta?</h1>
      <p class="lead">Zwi Mojzeszowicz, 74 anos, vai descobrir.</p>
      <p class="facts">Campinas → Manaus, pela costa.<br><span>9.000 km · 90 dias · sozinho.</span></p>
      <a class="cta" href="#apoiar">Apadrinhe um dia →</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ============ QUEM ============ -->
  <section class="quem rv">
    <p class="eyebrow">Quem pedala</p>
    <p class="role">Aventureiro · Escritor · Ativista ecológico</p>
    <p class="quote">“Terra ‘Gaia’ é Nossa Casa, Não Tem Plano B.”</p>
    <figure class="figute">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Zwi ajoelhado ao lado de um senhor idoso numa rua da cidade velha de Jerusalém, partindo pão">
      <figcaption>Jerusalém, ciclo-viagem por Israel. Recebe comida e teto dos humildes com gratidão.</figcaption>
    </figure>
    <p>Cuidou da família e do ofício até o fim do século passado. De lá pra cá vive para realizar sonhos: sai pedalando da porta de casa, sem equipe, sem traslado, dispensando o conforto que os amigos precisam. Lê seu livro para crianças por onde passa.</p>
    <p class="quote">“Vivo o dia sem pensar no amanhã.”</p>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ ESTRADA JA PERCORRIDA ============ -->
  <section class="estrada night rv"><div class="stars"></div>
    <p class="eyebrow">As estradas já percorridas</p>
    <h2 class="disp" style="font-size:clamp(1.9rem,7vw,2.5rem);margin-bottom:6px">Não é o primeiro salto.<br>É o maior.</h2>
    <p style="color:#b9c6ee;margin:14px 0 22px">Antes de encarar o Norte, ele já tinha desenhado meio continente no mapa.</p>
